TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select distinct lugx.group_id as value, lugx.group_name as name from BPM_USR_RUNTIME_PROPS burp, LSW_USR_XREF lux, LSW_USR_GRP_MEM_XREF lugmx, lsw_usr_grp_xref lugx where BURP.USER_ID(+) = LUX.USER_ID and lux.user_id = lugmx.user_id and lugx.group_id = lugmx.group_id and lugx.group_type != 1 order by lugx.group_id
